# PointOfNeed

IDS Point of Need allows users to include an icon with a tooltip to provide additional information on PointOfNeed labels

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/point-of-need
```

```tsx
import { PointOfNeed } from '@ids-ts/point-of-need';
```

## Props

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `message` | `string` | Yes | Tooltip message content. |
| `position` | `'left' \| 'right' \| 'top' \| 'bottom'` | No | Tooltip position relative to the icon. |
| `alignment` | `string` | No | Alignment of the tooltip. |
| `enableClickAway` | `boolean` | No | Closes tooltip on outside click when true. |
| `duration` | `number` | No | Auto-close duration in ms (0 = no auto-close). |
| `delayOpen` | `boolean` | No | Delays tooltip opening. |
| `delayOpenDuration` | `number` | No | Delay duration in ms when `delayOpen` is true. |

